(1,1,1,'N','<p>The Project Meeting Review Committee plays a critical role in ensuring the effective evaluation and progression of projects. Members of the committee are responsible for reviewing project proposals, assessing progress, and providing actionable feedback.</p>\r\n','<p>They outline the objectives, key deliverables, and the processes required to achieve the intended outcomes. The ToR specifies the roles and responsibilities of participants, the timelines for activities, and the resources available for implementation.</p>\r\n','admin','2024-11-23',NULL,NULL),
