(2,'LRDE',2,2,'LRDE/PRJ-1/EB/12JUN2024/2',1,0,0,0,'2024-06-12','10:00:00','MMA','N',NULL,'Kalam Conference hall','2','','Key components of the DMDDS include high-resolution cameras, ground-penetrating radar (GPR), and other sensor technologies capable of identifying buried or concealed mines with precision. These sensors enable the UAVs to survey large areas quickly and accurately, providing real-time data to mine clearance teams for analysis and action.','N','N','INI',NULL,'admin','2024-11-23 16:40:16','1024','2025-02-12 18:46:38',1,'N',NULL),
