(62,14,1,6,0,0,'<p><strong>11. Team Collaboration:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>How well did the team collaborate and build on each other&rsquo;s ideas?</li>\r\n	<li>Were there any noticeable gaps in teamwork or communication?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>12. Risk Assessment/Challenges:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Were potential risks identified during the meeting (e.g., delays, resource shortages)?</li>\r\n	<li>What actions were proposed to address these challenges?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>13. Satisfaction and Feedback:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>How satisfied were the attendees with the meeting&rsquo;s effectiveness?</li>\r\n	<li>Any feedback on how future meetings could be improved (e.g., more time for discussion, clearer agenda)?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 15:09:38',NULL,NULL,'Remarks'),
