(67,20,1,1,0,0,'<p>Air-to-air missiles (AAMs) represent the cutting edge of aerial combat technology, embodying precision, agility, and lethality. These sophisticated weapons are specifically designed for engagement between aircraft, enabling pilots to engage enemy targets from beyond visual range (BVR) or in close-range dogfights.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:38:15',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(68,20,1,2,0,0,'<p>AAMs come in various types, including short-range, medium-range, and beyond-visual-range missiles, each tailored to specific operational requirements and aircraft platforms. Equipped with advanced guidance systems, such as radar, infrared, or semi-active homing, AAMs can track and intercept enemy aircraft with remarkable accuracy, even in dynamic and challenging aerial environments.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:38:22',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(69,20,1,6,0,0,'<p>The evolution of AAMs has transformed aerial warfare, providing pilots with potent tools to dominate the skies and maintain air superiority. As nations continue to invest in AAM development, the future promises even greater advancements in speed, range, and precision, further solidifying the role of air-to-air missiles as indispensable assets in modern air combat operations.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:38:46',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(70,20,1,4,0,0,'<p>Development efforts in AAM technology focus on improving missile speed, maneuverability, range, and seeker capabilities, as well as enhancing resistance to electronic countermeasures.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:38:58',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(71,20,1,5,0,0,'Reduce size and weight of missile components for improved aerodynamics and performance.','A','','admin','2025-01-31 17:39:19',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(72,19,1,1,0,0,'<p>The Air Defence Fire Control Radar (ADFCR) project is a cornerstone in the development of comprehensive air defense systems aimed at safeguarding airspace sovereignty and protecting critical assets from aerial threats.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:39:51',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(73,19,1,2,0,0,'<p>These radar systems serve as the nerve center of integrated air defense networks, detecting, tracking, and guiding interceptor missiles to neutralize hostile aircraft, missiles, and unmanned aerial vehicles.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:39:59',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(74,19,1,4,0,0,'<p>The success of ADFCR projects relies on rigorous testing, validation, and integration with existing air defense assets, including command and control systems, surface-to-air missile batteries, and fighter aircraft.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:40:09',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(75,19,1,6,0,0,'<p>As the threat landscape continues to evolve with the emergence of stealth technology, hypersonic weapons, and unmanned aerial systems, the ADFCR project must adapt and innovate to maintain superiority in detecting and neutralizing emerging aerial threats effectively. Continued investment in research, development, and modernization efforts is critical to ensuring the readiness and effectiveness of air defense systems in countering evolving airborne threats and safeguarding national interests.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:40:20',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(76,22,1,1,0,0,'<p>Missile development involves a multifaceted process encompassing design, engineering, testing, and production to create advanced projectile systems for various purposes, including defense, space exploration, and scientific research</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:56:34',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(77,22,1,2,0,0,'<p>Initially, conceptualization begins with defining the missile&#39;s intended function and capabilities, considering factors such as range, payload capacity, speed, and maneuverability.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:56:46',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(78,22,1,6,0,0,'<p>Finally, operational deployment involves integration with broader defense systems or space exploration initiatives, marking the culmination of extensive development efforts aimed at delivering cutting-edge missile capabilities</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:56:57',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(79,22,1,4,0,0,'<p>Prototyping and testing play a crucial role in validating these designs, often through simulated environments and controlled trials to assess performance and reliability.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:57:06',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(80,22,1,3,23,9,'Prototyping and testing','A','','admin','2025-01-31 17:57:22',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(81,22,1,3,23,9,'Design and Engineering','A','','admin','2025-01-31 17:57:33',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(82,21,1,1,0,0,'<p>Ballistic missiles represent a formidable category of weapons with the capability to deliver devastating payloads across vast distances with remarkable speed and precision. Operating on the principle of a ballistic trajectory, these missiles are propelled into space before descending upon their targets along a predetermined path dictated by gravity and inertia.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:58:22',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(83,21,1,2,0,0,'<p>Intercontinental Ballistic Missiles (ICBMs) are the most prominent subclass, possessing the capacity to traverse continents in a matter of minutes, making them a potent tool for long-range strategic deterrence. Medium-Range Ballistic Missiles (MRBMs) and Short-Range Ballistic Missiles (SRBMs) serve more localized purposes, offering flexible options for regional conflicts and tactical operations.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:58:32',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(84,21,1,4,0,0,'<p>Ballistic missiles can carry conventional or nuclear warheads, presenting a grave threat to military targets, population centers, and critical infrastructure. Their deployment often signifies a significant escalation in hostilities and can provoke international tensions due to their potential for catastrophic destruction.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:58:43',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(85,21,1,6,0,0,'<p>Consequently, ballistic missile defense systems have become a crucial component of national security strategies, aimed at intercepting and neutralizing incoming threats. Despite efforts to curb proliferation and enhance deterrence measures, the ongoing development and deployment of ballistic missile technology underscore its enduring role as a pivotal force in shaping global geopolitics and security dynamics.</p>\r\n','C',NULL,'admin','2025-01-31 17:58:50',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
(86,21,1,3,22,9,'Conduct rigorous flight testing and range safety evaluations to validate performance and\r\nsafety.','A','','admin','2025-01-31 17:59:10',NULL,NULL,'Nil'),
