(1,'N',0,0,1,1,'2024-11-25','Project MOM','The objectives of this mission are primarily technological and include design, realization and launch of a Mars Orbiter spacecraft capable of operating with sufficient autonomy during the journey phase; Mars orbit insertion / capture and in-orbit phase around Mars. MOM carries five scientific payloads to study the Martian surface features, morphology, mineralogy and Martian atmosphere.','2025-01-01','2026-05-31',16,'USER','',460000000.00,'Mars continues to be an object of keen interest to scientists in the context of planetary evolution and extra-terrestrial life. Based on our understanding of Mars, which was thought to be probably a warm and wet planet earlier, is now seen to be dry with a thin atmosphere.','Y','2024-11-25','RMA','admin','2024-11-25 11:20:02',NULL,NULL,1),
(2,'N',0,0,2,NULL,NULL,'Project SONAR','The SONAR project focuses on enhancing operational efficiency and decision-making by providing advanced data analysis, real-time monitoring, and actionable insights. It leverages innovative technologies to ensure accuracy, scalability, and security in handling diverse datasets. Designed to cater to the needs of modern enterprises, the system integrates seamlessly with existing infrastructures, promoting transparency and streamlined workflows. Key features include automated reporting, dynamic visualization tools, and robust alert mechanisms to proactively address potential issues. The project aims to empower users with intuitive interfaces and reliable analytics to drive strategic growth and improve overall performance.','2025-02-19','2026-02-26',12,'DVD','',370000000.00,'The scope of the SONAR project encompasses the development and implementation of a comprehensive solution for data monitoring, analysis, and reporting. It aims to address critical needs across various domains, including real-time data acquisition, processing, and visualization. The project will integrate seamlessly with existing systems, ensuring compatibility and scalability to support growing organizational requirements.','N',NULL,'RIN','admin','2024-11-25 11:23:48',NULL,NULL,1),
(3,'N',0,0,5,1,'2025-01-31','Project Brahmashirsha ','The Brahmashirsha is a supreme and invincible divine weapon, revered for its unparalleled destructive power. Created by Lord Brahma, it holds the ability to eradicate entire armies, obliterate enemies, and reshape the very fabric of existence. Harnessing the ultimate energy of creation, the Brahmashirsha is capable of overwhelming any defense, making it one of the most fearsome astras in the ancient scriptures. When invoked, it unleashes a devastating force that can annihilate both physical and spiritual realms. Designed to be wielded only in the direst of circumstances, this weapon requires immense control and wisdom, as its power is boundless and irreversible. Its unparalleled potency reflects the supreme authority of Lord Brahma, ensuring its place as a symbol of cosmic might and divine justice.','2025-01-31','2026-01-01',11,'USER','',12345.00,' Certainly! Here?s a revised version:  The scope of the Brahmashirsha encompasses the creation and utilization of a divine weapon capable of immense destructive power. It is designed to serve as a last-resort solution in situations of extreme crisis, where other means of conflict resolution fail. The weapon?s activation involves intricate spiritual practices and supreme concentration, harnessing the energy of Lord Brahma himself. It aims to deliver a precise and catastrophic impact, capable of neutralizing the most formidable threats. The Brahmashirsha, while unparalleled in strength, requires the utmost wisdom and ethical responsibility to wield, ensuring that its use is both justified and controlled. Its impact reaches beyond the physical, influencing the very balance of cosmic order.','Y','2025-01-31','RMA','admin','2025-01-31 12:04:25','admin','2025-01-31 12:04:54',1);

